						               													<description>Card game combining memory and risk taking with a cooperative version.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The cards &amp;quot;the wolf arrives&amp;quot; are placed face up, each player receives a house card and we place all other cards face down on the table. Each player in turn returns as many cards as he wishes in order to reveal and recover the animals from his house. But he must stop and win nothing if he returns a card he has already revealed or if he returns a wolf card. In the latter case he returns a card &amp;quot;the wolf arrives&amp;quot;, unless he returned a card clover. When a player has collected the 4 animals from his house, he puts the cards aside and draws a new house. The game is over when all the cards &amp;quot;the wolf arrives&amp;quot; are returned or when all the animals are safe. This is the player with the most cards &amp;quot;animal&amp;quot; who wins. In the cooperative version the players play together against the wolf!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
